title: Totally.Unbalanced-HI2U
description:
Totally Unbalanced (c) OtakuMaker.com

Release 29/07/2016

Protection: Steam

Game Size: 1 DISC

Game Type: Action, Adventure, Casual, Indie, Racing

RELEASE NOTES

Totally Unbalanced is a 3D platform game where you have to
complete puzzles and overcome obstacles. Totally Unbalanced also
features (currently) two multiplayer modes : sumo arena with 4
players and racing mode with 16 players

INSTALL NOTES

1  Unpack
2  Mount / burn image
3  Install
4  Copy content from 'Crack' folder and replace game dir files
5  Play game
6  If U like it, buy it
